title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, East Market]
description: Creeping vines and a thick growth of low-lying grass extends across a large space of ground that was probably once a huge open market where the inhabitants of the city could hawk their assorted produce and wares.  To the east the flattened tip of a tall tower pokes its black silhouette above the dark, jagged outline of a series of walls.

Creeping vines and a thick growth of low-lying grass extends across a large space of ground that was probably once a huge open market where the inhabitants of the city could hawk their assorted produce and wares.  To the east the flattened tip of a tall tower rises high above a series of walls and roofless buildings.
